OL,6,FPolice are searching three more
OL,7,Flocations in connection to a murder
OL,8,Finvestigation launched after a torso
OL,9,Fwas found in a beauty spot.
OL,11,FThe remains of Stuart Everett, 67,
OL,12,Fwere found scattered around areas of
OL,13,FSalford, Greater Manchester, in April.
OL,15,FMr Everett is thought to have died at
OL,16,Fan address in the Winton area of
OL,17,FManchester at the end of March before
OL,18,Fparts of his body were discovered in
OL,19,Ffour different areas.
