OL,3,CPolice searching more locations after
OL,4,Chuman remains found
OL,6,FNow, following CCTV and phone data
OL,7,Finvestigations officers, from (GMP)
OL,8,Fhave begun searching three more areas.
OL,10,FBoggart Hole Clough, in Blackley,
OL,11,FNorth Manchester, land near Patricroft
OL,12,Ftrain station in Eccles, and land near
OL,13,FWalkden train station in Worsley, both
OL,14,Fin Salford, have all been cordoned off.
OL,16,FSpecialist divers, Tactical Aid Unit
OL,17,Fofficers and police dogs will be used
OL,18,Fin the searches.
