OL,4,Chuman remains found
OL,6,FMr Everett's remains were discovered
OL,7,Fby a passer-by in Kersal Dale park,
OL,8,FSalford, wrapped in clear plastic on 4
OL,9,FApril.
OL,11,FRemains were also found at by
OL,12,Fresidents in two more locations on 27,
OL,13,F28 April, at Blackleach Reservoir and
OL,14,FLinneyshaw Colliery Wood, and by
OL,15,Fpolice on 30 April in an alleyway
OL,16,Fclose to railway lines off Worsley
OL,17,FRoad, all in Salford.
