OL,3,CPolice searching more locations after
OL,4,Chuman remains found
OL,6,FMichal Jaroslaw Polchowski, 70, and
OL,7,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, of Worsley
OL,8,FRoad, Eccles, have been charged with
OL,9,FMr Everett's murder.
OL,11,FBoth were remanded in custody after
OL,12,Fappearing at Manchester Crown Court
OL,13,Fand will next appear in court on 18
OL,14,FJuly for a plea and trial preparation
OL,15,Fhearing.
OL,17,FA provisional trial date of 3 March
OL,18,F2025 was fixed by Judge Nicholas Dean
OL,19,FKC, the Honorary Recorder of
OL,20,FManchester.
