OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Lewis Hughes,
OL,7,Ffrom GMP's Serious Crime Division and
OL,8,FSenior Investigating Officer, said:
OL,9,F"The scenes that we will be searching
OL,10,Fover the coming days have come to our
OL,11,Fattention through some exceptional
OL,12,Fdetective work conducted by the
OL,13,Finvestigation team.
OL,15,F"We know there will be some disruption
OL,16,Fto the local community as a result of
OL,17,Fsearching other locations, but it is
OL,18,Fso important that we do this, we need
OL,19,Fto be able to provide Stuart's family
OL,20,Fwith the information they need to
OL,21,Fprocess this news.
