OL,6,F"Our investigation is ongoing, we
OL,7,Fstill have a lot of work to do and I
OL,8,Fhope the public can see the dedication
OL,9,Fand compassion that continues to be
OL,10,Fshown across the force by officers and
OL,11,Fstaff who are either keeping the scene
OL,12,Fsecure, searching for evidence or
OL,13,Finvestigating this behind the scenes `
OL,14,Fwe all have our part to play in
OL,15,Fgetting justice for Stuart's family
OL,16,Fand every search we conduct is one
OL,17,Fstep closer to finding answers for
OL,18,Fthem."
OL,20,FIn a Mr Everett's family said they
OL,21,Fwere "united in grief".
