OL,6,F"We as a family are united in our
OL,7,Fgrief over the devastating news of
OL,8,FStuart's untimely death and the manner
OL,9,Fin which he died," the family said.
OL,11,F"He was a unique and endearing
OL,12,Fcharacter who always put his family
OL,13,Fand many friends first.
OL,15,F"He loved his food, his garden, his
OL,16,Fmusic and a flutter on the horses, we
OL,17,Fhave been overwhelmed with the
OL,18,Fmessages of support and are thankful
OL,19,Fthat so many people thought so much of
OL,20,Fhim.
